  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lumi Trek is a unique rhythm platformer where you have to combine the three primary colors of light to overcome obstacles.</strong> Change the color of the moving star at the right time, and stay calm when deadly traps appear. It may sound simple, but this challenge will make your hands sweat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn how to change the color of the star!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The three primary colors of light are red, green and blue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combining the red, green and blue lights will turn the star into various colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can turn on and off the colors of light to change the color of the star as you wish.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=450 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Break through blocks of various colors!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The star will fly towards one of the nearby blocks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the star hits the block, if both the star and the blocks are different colors, life decreases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to change the color of the star so that it matches the block before it hits. It's time to show off your reflexes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Don't panic when facing traps!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trap blocks will interfere with your play in various ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By staying calm, you will be able to easily overcome these traps. Trust your eyes and hands.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't get frustrated if you make a mistake. Challenge yourself once again to beat it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red, green, blue... You only need to hit these three buttons to play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an intuitive and creative gameplay with colorful adventure stages and great music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also challenge the limits of your concentration through endless challenge stages.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lumi Trek is a unique rhythm platformer where you have to combine the three primary colors of light to overcome obstacles.</strong> Change the color of the moving star at the right time, and stay calm when deadly traps appear. It may sound simple, but this challenge will make your hands sweat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn how to change the color of the star!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The three primary colors of light are red, green and blue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combining the red, green and blue lights will turn the star into various colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can turn on and off the colors of light to change the color of the star as you wish.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=450 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/f49dee2b0a2f6c67989cf80de74766d0.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Break through blocks of various colors!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The star will fly towards one of the nearby blocks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the star hits the block, if both the star and the blocks are different colors, life decreases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to change the color of the star so that it matches the block before it hits. It's time to show off your reflexes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/b60a34876f0f8734e6d90a56d670f834.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Don't panic when facing traps!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trap blocks will interfere with your play in various ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By staying calm, you will be able to easily overcome these traps. Trust your eyes and hands.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't get frustrated if you make a mistake. Challenge yourself once again to beat it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.poster.avif?t=1741885994\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.webm?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363410/extras/97be25f0663c9ba9bc8d3cfe2bb49318.mp4?t=1741885994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red, green, blue... You only need to hit these three buttons to play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an intuitive and creative gameplay with colorful adventure stages and great music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also challenge the limits of your concentration through endless challenge stages.</p></li></ul>",
